issues.title: Tomb door in the wrath of the mummy quest not working
issues.body:
I was trying to to the wrath of the mummy quest and when i came to the tomb door i had to work out the code which is 63814275 (or so i thought) i put it in, it didnt work so i tried again and it still didnt work so i went to th wiki and searched it up, i had gotten the code right it turned out but the door just wouldent open, i even tried changing servers. please fix this bug asap please thx.
P.S. Sorry for my bad grammar

issues.title: Cloud particle effect looks like the letter effect #1704
issues.body: I recently bought the cloud particle effect for my player in-game, BeforEtho. For some reason, the cloud effect does not work, it turns out looking like the letter effect and says that I've equipped the letter effect. Any ideas?
issues.answer: You need to use photon particle goodness!
